NAME
    Pod::Weaver::Section::BashCompletion::PerinciCmdLine - Add a BASH
    COMPLETION section for Perinci::CmdLine-based scripts

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.01 of
    Pod::Weaver::Section::BashCompletion::PerinciCmdLine (from Perl
    distribution Pod-Weaver-Section-BashCompletion-PerinciCmdLine), released
    on 2014-11-08.

SYNOPSIS
    In your "weaver.ini":

     [BashCompletion::PerinciCmdLine]

DESCRIPTION
    This section plugin adds a BASH COMPLETION section for
    Perinci::CmdLine-based scripts. The section contains information on how
    to activate bash completion for the scripts.

SEE ALSO
    Perinci::CmdLine

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Pod-Weaver-Section-BashCompletion-PerinciC
    mdLine>.

